msgctxt "116_Man"
msgid "Excuse me, do you know who I am? I can't remember anything..."
msgstr "¿Perdona, sabes quién soy? No recuerdo nada..."

msgctxt "128_Man"
msgid "Wait, I do remember something... I used to beat the crap out of people on the street..."
msgstr "Espera, recuerdo algo... Solía ​​dar palizas a la gente en la calle..."

msgctxt "152_Man"
msgid "Stop, stop! I remember now, I remember everything!"
msgstr "¡Para, para! Ahora lo recuerdo, lo recuerdo todo!"

msgctxt "164_Man"
msgid "P-Please, take this if you'd like! You cured my amnesia, after all..."
msgstr "¡Po-Porfavor, toma esto si quieres! Después de todo has curado mi amnesia..."

msgctxt "176_Man"
msgid "You got a nice %s."
msgstr "Obtuviste un %s."

msgctxt "212_Man"
msgid "I think those punches mighta actually given me brain damage..."
msgstr "Creo que esos puñetazos podrían haberme provocado daños cerebrales..."

